title: NFL ATL: Rookie Bests and Busts, Week 7 TNF preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Rookie Bests and Busts, Week 7 TNF preview
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling catch you up on the latest news from around the league and give you their rookie bests and busts of the 2013 season. The gang also previews the “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the Seattle Seahawks and Arizona Cardinals. Find out which team they stick a fork in this week. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
